reviewText: Outlaw ghosts are on the loose too bad it takes over half of the move for them to actually do anything. Mostly it appears to be a our collage vacation in the country video. and I'm not kidding more then half of the movie focuses on these collage friends. There is no mention of any impending danger. I give it three stars because it does start out pretty good and our starlet is not to bad looking, she at least acts like she at least has half a brain.
